Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.77,0:21:12.37,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}昨日も今日も晴天で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.38,0:21:15.08,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}入道雲を見ていた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.11,0:21:17.78,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}怠いくらいの快晴だ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:20.60,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}徐に目を閉じて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.60,0:21:23.14,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}「それ」はどうも簡単に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:25.83,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}思い出せやしない様で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.87,0:21:28.40,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}年を取った現状に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.40,0:21:30.75,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}浸ってたんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.17,0:21:44.70,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}大人ぶった作戦で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.77,0:21:47.42,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}不思議な合図立てて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:50.10,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}「行こうか、今日も戦争だ」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.11,0:21:52.97,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}立ち向かって　手を取った
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.97,0:21:55.47,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}理不尽なんて当然で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.51,0:21:58.19,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}独りぼっち　強いられて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.27,0:21:59.69,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,0)}迷った僕は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.69,0:22:03.06,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(0,300)}憂鬱になりそうになってさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.78,0:22:06.16,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}背高草を分けて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.52,0:22:09.03,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}滲む太陽睨んで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.20,0:22:11.50,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}君はさ、こう言ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,0:22:14.57,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}「孤独だったら、おいでよ」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.59,0:22:17.00,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}騒がしさがノックして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.31,0:22:19.79,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}生まれた　感情さえも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.92,0:22:22.79,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}頭に浮かんでは萎んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.79,0:22:24.61,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}「{\c&HFFF30B&\3c&H948E20&}幻{\r}なのかな？」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.34,0:22:27.86,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}秘密基地に集まって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.91,0:22:30.57,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}「楽しいね」って単純な
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.63,0:22:33.29,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}あの頃を思い出して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.29,0:22:35.63,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}話をしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.03,0:22:38.66,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}秘密基地に集まって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.72,0:22:41.37,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}笑い合った夏の日に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.41,0:22:44.09,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}「また何処かで思い出して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.09,0:22:46.40,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,0)}出逢えるかな」って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.40,0:22:49.05,OPJP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(0,300)}何度でも描こう
