Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.77,0:21:12.37,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}昨天和今天都是晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.38,0:21:15.08,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}望著那積雨雲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.11,0:21:17.78,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}天空萬里無雲得令人發倦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:20.60,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}徐徐閉上雙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.60,0:21:23.14,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}總覺得「那個」好像
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:25.83,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}並不是那麼簡單就能回想得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.87,0:21:28.40,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}不斷長大的現狀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.40,0:21:30.75,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}已陷入其中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.17,0:21:44.70,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}在裝作大人的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.77,0:21:47.42,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}打著不可思議的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:50.10,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}「走吧，今天也是戰爭呀」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.11,0:21:52.97,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}勇敢面對　手牽手地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.97,0:21:55.47,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}因為不講理什麼的是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.51,0:21:58.19,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}孤身一人  強迫如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.27,0:21:59.69,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,0)}曾而迷惘的我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.69,0:22:03.06,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(0,300)}好像要變得憂鬱起來呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.78,0:22:06.16,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}撥開高草
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.52,0:22:09.03,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}虛眼看著模糊的太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.20,0:22:11.50,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}你呀  那樣說了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,0:22:14.57,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}「如果孤獨的話  就過來吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.59,0:22:17.00,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}喧鬧向我敲門
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.31,0:22:19.79,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}就連產生出的　這份感情也
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.92,0:22:22.79,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}浮現腦海而又枯萎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.79,0:22:24.61,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}「是{\c&HFFF30B&\3c&H948E20&}幻{\r}覺嗎？」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.34,0:22:27.86,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}聚集在秘密基地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.91,0:22:30.57,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}說著「真快樂呀」真是單純呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.63,0:22:33.29,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}回憶起那些日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.29,0:22:35.63,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}來聊聊天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.03,0:22:38.66,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}聚集在秘密基地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.72,0:22:41.37,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}在一同歡笑的夏日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.41,0:22:44.09,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}「能又再在某處回憶起來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.09,0:22:46.40,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,0)}再次相遇的吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.40,0:22:49.05,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(0,300)}不論多少次　如此描繪吧
